---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="เครื่องคำนวณการเงินยอดนิยม 10 อันดับ — ภาษี เงินเดือน สินเชื่อ | Kamnuanlek"
  description="รวม 10 เครื่องคำนวณการเงินที่คนไทยใช้บ่อยที่สุด ภาษีเงินได้ เงินเดือนสุทธิ ผ่อนบ้าน ผ่อนรถ ดอกเบี้ย ใช้ฟรีทุกตัว อัปเดตปี 2569"
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">เครื่องคำนวณการเงินยอดนิยม 10 อันดับ</h1>

    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12">
      Master your money with these 10 must-use financial tools. From tax planning to loan management, these calculators help you make smarter financial decisions.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">1</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Thai Income Tax Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Calculate your annual income tax accurately with deductions and allowances. Essential for self-employed, freelancers, and salaried professionals.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณภาษีเงินได้บุคคลธรรมดา/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate Tax →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">2</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Home Loan Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Plan your mortgage with accurate monthly payment calculations. Compare different loan terms and interest rates before buying your home.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณผ่อนบ้าน/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate Payment →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">3</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Savings Interest Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">See how your savings grow over time. Compare interest rates and deposit amounts to maximize your returns.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณดอกเบี้ยเงินฝาก/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate Interest →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">4</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Car Loan Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Plan your vehicle purchase with accurate monthly installments. Calculate total cost and compare financing options.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณผ่อนรถ/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate Payment →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">5</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Personal Loan Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Calculate monthly payments for personal loans. Understand total interest cost and plan your repayment strategy.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณผ่อนกู้/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate Payment →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">6</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">VAT Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Calculate Value Added Tax (7%) for business transactions. Essential tool for business owners and VAT-registered companies.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณมูลค่าเพิ่ม/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate VAT →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">7</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Salary Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Calculate net salary after tax and deductions. Understand your take-home pay and income tax obligations.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณเงินเดือน/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate Salary →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">8</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Investment Return Calculator (ROI)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Calculate returns on your investments. Compare different investment opportunities and track growth over time.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณ-roi/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate ROI →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">9</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Compound Interest Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Understand the power of compound interest. See how your money grows with regular deposits and reinvested interest.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณดอกเบี้ยทบต้น/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate Compound Interest →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">10</div>
        <div class="flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Retirement Planning Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Plan your retirement with confidence. Calculate how much you need to save and when you can retire comfortably.</p>
          <a href="/คำนวณเงินเกษียณ/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Calculate Retirement →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Use These Calculators?</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">✓</span>
          <span><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Get precise calculations for tax planning and financial decisions</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">✓</span>
          <span><strong>Save Money:</strong> Make informed decisions to maximize savings and minimize taxes</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">✓</span>
          <span><strong>Free & Fast:</strong> No sign-up required, instant results</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">✓</span>
          <span><strong>Thai-Specific:</strong> Designed for Thai tax laws and financial systems</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Explore More Calculators</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/ตัวช่วยคำนวณการเงิน/" class="p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 transition-colors">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">💳 Financial Calculators Hub</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">Complete collection of all financial tools</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/เปรียบเทียบเครื่องคำนวณภาษี/" class="p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 transition-colors">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">📊 Tax Calculator Comparison</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">Compare different types of tax calculators</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/เปรียบเทียบสินเชื่อ/" class="p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 transition-colors">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">🏦 Loan Comparison Guide</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">Compare home, car, and personal loans</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/วิธีคำนวณภาษีเงินได้ไทย/" class="p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 transition-colors">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">📚 Thai Income Tax Guide</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">Step-by-step guide to calculating income tax</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
